        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">Common Violations in San Antonio</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8"><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Expired tags in River Walk hotel and restaurant operations — high volume and multiple buildings create systematic tracking challenges</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class K extinguishers in Texas Medical Center institutional kitchen facilities</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Missing Class C coverage in sensitive hospital and research laboratory environments</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-red-light rounded-lg border border-red-200"><span class="text-red-brand font-bold flex-shrink-0">!</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Inadequate Class B coverage in military base support facilities near Fort Sam Houston and Lackland AFB</span></div></div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">San Antonio Fire Prevention Contacts</h2>
